✅ 1. Create the Project Folder
mkdir gateway-demo
cd gateway-demo

✅ 2. Install FastAPI + Uvicorn

(Required for building the API server)

pip install fastapi uvicorn

✅ 3. (Optional) Install Requests Library

(Used by the gateway simulator to send HTTP POST)

pip install requests

✅ 4. Run the FastAPI Server

Inside the project folder:

uvicorn api_server:app --reload


This starts your local API at:

http://127.0.0.1:8000

✅ 5. Run the Gateway Simulator

Open a second terminal:

python gateway_simulator.py


This sends JSON every 5 seconds to your server.
